---
layout: base.njk
title: Articles
description: Analysis and dispatches on the LIHTC expiration crisis, written by tenants.
pagination:
  data: collections.articles
  size: 50
  alias: posts
permalink: /articles/
---
<header class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">Articles</div>
    <h1>Analysis &amp; dispatches</h1>
    <p class="deck">Written by tenants living through it. Everything sourced, every source named.</p>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="section">
  <div class="container">
    {% if posts.length %}
    <div class="cards">
      {% for post in posts %}
      <a class="card" href="{{ post.url }}">
        <div class="meta">{{ post.data.tag or "Article" }} · {{ post.data.date | readableDate }}</div>
        <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <div class="more">Read →</div>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <p class="lead">Nothing published yet.</p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</main>
